3. affaan-m/everything-claude-code (ECC) — https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code
   License: MIT
   Adopted in:
     - templates/claude/hooks/verification_loop.py        (from skills/verification-loop/SKILL.md)
       — adapted the "lint/typecheck/syntax-check loop after every Edit"
         pattern to a PostToolUse hook that nudges MCP probes per
         `addon_globs` config. Toolkit-side additions: per-file 30s
         dedupe, framework-overlay config split (verification.<fw>.json),
         emit_fire_event integration.
     - templates/claude/commands/eval-define.md           (from skills/eval-harness/SKILL.md
                                                          + skills/agent-eval/SKILL.md)
     - templates/claude/commands/eval-backfill.md         (from skills/eval-harness/SKILL.md)
       — "concrete pass/fail criteria written into spec frontmatter
         BEFORE /implement so /verify becomes mechanical" pattern.
         Toolkit-side additions: integration with .agent-toolkit/
         specs/<slug>.md frontmatter schema; acceptance_evals field
         honored by verify_lint Stop hook.
     - templates/claude/commands/bug-to-test.md           (from skills/ai-regression-testing/SKILL.md)
       — "write tests for bugs found, not for code that works" rule.
         Toolkit-side additions: auto-register an invariant in
         invariants.json so future Edits cannot strip the test.

